msgid "rabbit mutagen"
msgid_plural "rabbit mutagens"
msgstr[0] "兔子诱变剂"

#. ~ Mutation class name
#: .\EMM_mutation_category.json .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid "Crab"
msgstr "螃蟹"

#. ~ Mutation class: Crab mutagen_message
#: .\EMM_mutation_category.json
msgid "You suddenly want to start walking sideways."
msgstr "你突然想开始横着走。"

#. ~ Mutation class: Crab iv_message
#: .\EMM_mutation_category.json
msgid "You clench your fists uncontrollably."
msgstr "你不由自主地握紧了拳头。"

#. ~ Mutation class: Crab Male memorial messsage
#: .\EMM_mutation_category.json
msgctxt "memorial_male"
msgid "Got crabs."
msgstr "感染了螃蟹。"

#. ~ Mutation class: Crab Female memorial messsage
#: .\EMM_mutation_category.json
msgctxt "memorial_female"
msgid "Got crabs."
msgstr "感染了螃蟹。"

#. ~ Mutation class name
#: .\EMM_mutation_category.json .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid "Snake"
msgstr "蛇"

#. ~ Mutation class: Snake mutagen_message
#: .\EMM_mutation_category.json
msgid "You suddenly let out a hiss"
msgstr "你突然发出一声嘶嘶声"

#. ~ Mutation class: Snake iv_message
#: .\EMM_mutation_category.json
msgid "You feel like your body elongates."
msgstr "你感觉自己的身体在拉长。"

#. ~ Mutation class: Snake Male memorial messsage
#: .\EMM_mutation_category.json
msgctxt "memorial_male"
msgid "Slithered away."
msgstr "滑行离开。"

#. ~ Mutation class: Snake Female memorial messsage
#: .\EMM_mutation_category.json
msgctxt "memorial_female"
msgid "Slithered away."
msgstr "滑行离开。"

#. ~ Mutation class name
#: .\EMM_mutation_category.json .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid "Rabbit"
msgstr "兔子"

#. ~ Mutation class: Rabbit mutagen_message
#: .\EMM_mutation_category.json
msgid "You suddenly want to eat carrots."
msgstr "你突然想吃胡萝卜。"

#. ~ Mutation class: Rabbit iv_message
#: .\EMM_mutation_category.json
msgid "You feel like your nose starts twitching uncontrollably."
msgstr "你感觉自己的鼻子开始不受控制地抽动。"

#. ~ Mutation class: Rabbit Male memorial messsage
#: .\EMM_mutation_category.json
msgctxt "memorial_male"
msgid "Hopped away."
msgstr "蹦跳离开。"

#. ~ Mutation class: Rabbit Female memorial messsage
#: .\EMM_mutation_category.json
msgctxt "memorial_female"
msgid "Hopped away."
msgstr "蹦跳离开。"

#: .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid "Ecdysis"
msgstr "蜕皮"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Ecdysis'}
#: .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid ""
"If you feel like your exoskeleton is getting too tight, you may choose to "
"shed it. Doing so will produce chitin chunks, useful for crafting. Activate "
"to shed your carapace."
msgstr "如果你感觉自己的外骨骼变得太紧，可以选择将其蜕下。这样做会产生几丁质块，可用于制作。激活以蜕下你的甲壳。"

#: .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid "You shed your old exoskeleton. You are feeling fresh."
msgstr "你蜕下了旧的外骨骼。你感觉焕然一新。"

#: .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid "Chitinous Carapace"
msgstr "几丁质甲壳"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Chitinous Carapace'}
#: .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your body is covered with a thick, impenetrable red carapace. It provides "
"unmatched physical protection and even some protection from corrosive "
"chemicals, but reduces your dexterity by 3 and severely encumbers all body "
"parts but your eyes.  Greatly reduces wet effects."
msgstr ""
"你的身体覆盖着一层厚实、坚不可摧的红色甲壳。它提供了无与伦比的物理防护，甚至能抵御一些腐蚀性化学物质，但会使你的敏捷降低3点，并严重妨碍除眼睛外的所有身体部位。大幅减少潮湿效果。"

#: .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid "Giant Pincer"
msgstr "巨钳"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Giant Pincer'}
#: .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid ""
"Instead of your right hand, you now have a giant crab claw. It encumbers you"
" greatly, but you can occasionally use it in melee combat to deal massive "
"damage."
msgstr "你的右手现在变成了一只巨大的蟹钳。它会严重妨碍你，但偶尔可以在近战中使用它造成巨大伤害。"

#: .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid "You pinch %s with your giant claw"
msgstr "你用巨钳夹住了%s"

#: .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid "%1$s pinches %2$s with their giant claw"
msgstr "%1$s用巨钳夹住了%2$s"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Crab'}
#: .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid "Who needs skin when you can have a carapace?"
msgstr "有了甲壳，谁还需要皮肤呢？"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Snake'}
#: .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid "Who needssss legssss anyway?"
msgstr "谁还需要腿呢？"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Rabbit'}
#: .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid "You are so adorable!"
msgstr "你真可爱！"

#: .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid "Spider Eyes"
msgstr "蜘蛛眼"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Spider Eyes'}
#: .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid ""
"You have grown two extra sets of eyes on your forehead. This improves your "
"perception by 2, though other survivors may react badly."
msgstr "你的额头上长出了两对额外的眼睛。这使你的感知提高了2点，但其他幸存者可能会有不好的反应。"

#: .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid "Viper Fangs"
msgstr "毒蛇尖牙"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Viper Fangs'}
#: .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your teeth have grown into two-inch-long fangs, perfect for injecting venom."
" They allow you to make extra attacks when your mouth is uncovered."
msgstr "你的牙齿长成了两英寸长的尖牙，非常适合注射毒液。当你的嘴巴未被覆盖时，它们允许你进行额外攻击。"

#: .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid "You sink your fangs into %s"
msgstr "你将尖牙刺入%s"

#: .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid "%1$s sinks their fangs into %2$s"
msgstr "%1$s将尖牙刺入%2$s"

#: .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid "Deformed Legs"
msgstr "畸形腿"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Deformed Legs'}
#: .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid "Your legs are badly deformed. Permanent leg encumbrance."
msgstr "你的腿部严重畸形。永久性腿部负重。"

#: .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid "Serpentine Tail"
msgstr "蛇形尾"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Serpentine Tail'}
#: .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid ""
"A massive serpentine tail extends for some body lengths behind you, and your"
" legs and feet transformed into useless stumps, hanging off your sides. You "
"can use your tail to crush your enemies, when conditions favor it. Prevents "
"wearing pants and footgear."
msgstr ""
"一条巨大的蛇形尾巴从你身后延伸出数个体长，你的双腿和双脚已变成无用的残肢，悬垂在身体两侧。在条件有利时，你可以用尾巴碾压敌人。无法穿着裤子和鞋类。"

#: .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid "You crush %s with your coils"
msgstr "你用蛇身缠绕碾碎了%s"

#: .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid "%1$s crushes %2$s with their coils"
msgstr "%1$s用蛇身缠绕碾碎了%2$s"

#: .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid "Silent Movement"
msgstr "无声移动"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Silent Movement'}
#: .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid "You know how to move completely silently."
msgstr "你懂得如何完全无声地移动。"

#: .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid "Long Neck"
msgstr "长颈"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Long Neck'}
#: .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid "Your neck is unusually elongated.  This has no effect."
msgstr "你的脖子异常伸长。这没有实际效果。"

#: .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid "Cobra's Hood"
msgstr "眼镜蛇颈兜"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Cobra's Hood"}
#: .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid ""
"You have a hood on your neck, like a cobra's. It looks striking, but makes "
"you better at intimidating. Adds a slight head encumbrance."
msgstr "你的颈部有一个像眼镜蛇一样的颈兜。它看起来很醒目，但能让你更好地进行恐吓。略微增加头部负重。"

#: .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid "Soft Fur"
msgstr "柔软皮毛"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Soft Fur'}
#: .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid ""
"You've got an incredibly soft fur, and it's very pleasant to touch. It "
"provides some protection from cold, and makes persuading other survivors "
"easier."
msgstr "你拥有极其柔软的皮毛，触感非常舒适。它提供一定的寒冷防护，并使说服其他幸存者变得更容易。"

#: .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid "Rabbit Feet"
msgstr "兔脚"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Rabbit Feet'}
#: .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid ""
"Your feet have grown really big, and look exactly like a rabbit's. Prevents "
"wearing shoes."
msgstr "你的脚变得非常大，看起来完全像兔子的脚。无法穿鞋。"

#: .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid "Absent Minded"
msgstr "心不在焉"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Absent Minded'}
#: .\EMM_mutations.json
msgid ""
"You are not too bright, and you get distracted easily. Intelligence - 2"
msgstr "你不太聪明，且容易分心。智力 - 2"

#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Even More Mutations"
msgstr "更多突变"

#. ~ Description for Even More Mutations
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Adds three new mutation branches and minor changes to existing ones."
msgstr "新增三个突变分支，并对现有分支进行小幅调整。"
